 ohun ba se n po si ni soki ti a ba jusile nomba pato afida lati ibere itelentele ohun a le so ijinnasi togaju larin afida meji di kekere bo ba se wu wa itelentele cauchy fun awon nomba gidi itelentele kan fun nomba gidi je ti cauchy ti fun gbogbo nomba gidi alapaotun ti r nomba odidi n alapaotun yio wa fun won to je pe fun gbogbo awon nomba odidi m n n a ni ẹ ka áljẹ brà anigunmeta triangle je okan ninu ipilese irisi aniwonile anigunpupo polygon pelu elenusonso vertex meta ati egbe meta ti won apa ila line segment gbooro irisi yi lo mu eka imo isiro ti a mo si iwon anigunmeta trigonometry wa eyi fihan wa bi o se se pataki to orisirisi awon anigunmeta a le se eka anigunmeta gege bi ibu awon egbe won se to anigunmeta onibukanna equilateral triangle gbogbo egbe meteta ni won ni ibu kanna anigunmeta onibumeji isosceles triangle egbe meji nikan ni won ni ibu kanna anigunmeta onibumeta scalene triangle ibu otooto ni egbe meteta ni equilateral triangle isosceles triangle scalene triangle oníbùúkaánnàoníbùúméjìoníbùúmẹ ta a tun le se eka awon anigunmeta gege bi itobisi awon igun inu won se to anigunmeta onigunrege right angled triangle o ni igun kan to je aadorun iyi anigunmeta onigunsonso acute triangle igun meteta inu re kere ju lo anigunmeta onigunfenfe obtuse triangle o ni igun kan ti o tobi ju lo right triangle obtuse triangle acute triangle onígunrégéonígunfẹ nfẹ onígunsonso itokasi ẹ ka trigonomẹ trì ninu mathimatiki òbìrípo circle pelu arin c ati ilatotan r je irisi aniwonile to je akojopo awon ojuami ati ijinasi won si arin ti a n pe ni ilatotan radius iyipo je ila alajapo curve ti o ti ti o si pin pepe si apa inu ati ode ibu re ni a mo si ayika circumference inu re ni a n pe ni abọ disk ọfà arc si ni apa iwapapo pato kan lori iyipo na agbeyewo idogba fun iyipo ti a ba ni ona ipoidojuko x y iyipo to ni arin ni a b ati ilatotan r je akojopo gbogbo ojuami x y to fi je pe ti o ba je pe ni ojuibere origin ni arin re wa a le so afise dero bayi be si ni tangenti yio je nigbati si je ipoidojuko ojuami kanna won x y itokasi ẹ ka jíómẹ trì ẹ ka mathimátíkì january january january ìṣẹ lẹ ìbí sir francis bacon english philosopher d gotthold ephraim lessing german author and philosopher d george gordon byron th baron byron lord byron english poet d grigori rasputin russian monk d antonio gramsci italian philosopher and political theorist d u thant burmese rd united nations secretary general d sam cooke american singer d dj jazzy jeff american rapper and actor ikú lyndon b johnson ẹ ka january february february march march events bc romulus first king of rome celebrates the first roman triumph after his victory over the caeninenses following the rape of the sabine women bc lucius cornelius sulla at the head of a roman republic army enters athens removing the tyrant aristion who was supported by troops of mithridates vi of pontus roman emperor diocletian raises maximian to the rank of caesar roman emperors diocletian and maximian appoint constantius chlorus and galerius as caesares thus beginning the tetrarchy crispus and constantine ii sons of roman emperor constantine i and licinius iunior son of emperor licinius are made caesares the unitas fratrum is established in the village of kunvald on the bohemian moravian borderland it is to date the second oldest protestant denomination huguenots are massacred by catholics in wassy france marking the start of the french wars of religion the city of rio de janeiro is founded the uppsala synod is summoned to confirm the exact forms of the lutheran church of sweden writs issued in february by charles i of england mandate that every county in england not just seaport towns pay ship tax by this date samuel de champlain reclaims his role as commander of new france on behalf of cardinal richelieu georgeana massachusetts now known as york maine becomes the first incorporated city in the united states sarah good sarah osborne and tituba are brought before local magistrates in salem village massachusetts beginning what would become known as the salem witch trials sweden introduces its own swedish calendar in an attempt to gradually merge into the gregorian calendar reverts to the julian calendar on this date in and introduces the gregorian calendar on this date in the continental congress adopts the articles of confederation the first united states census is authorized ohio is admitted as the th u s state justice samuel chase is acquitted at the end of his impeachment trial by the u s senate leaders of the mameluke dynasty are killed by egyptian ruler muhammad ali napoleon returns to france from his banishment on elba a convention of delegates from texas communities convenes in washington on the brazos texas to deliberate independence from mexico adolphe thiers becomes prime minister of france president john tyler signs a bill authorizing the united states to annex the republic of texas the state of michigan formally abolishes capital punishment archibald william montgomerie th earl of eglinton is appointed lord lieutenant of ireland german psychologist friedrich eduard beneke disappears two years later his remains are found in a canal near charlottenburg nebraska becomes the th u s state lancaster nebraska is renamed lincoln and becomes the state capital marshal f s lópez dies during the battle of cerro corá thus marking the end of the war of the triple alliance yellowstone national park is established as the world s first national park e remington and sons in ilion new york begins production of the first practical typewriter the anglo chinese school singapore is founded by bishop william oldham nikola tesla gives the first public demonstration of radio in st louis missouri battle of adowa an ethiopian army defeats an outnumbered italian force ending the first italo ethiopian war henri becquerel discovers radioactivity the worst avalanche in united states history buries a great northern railway train in northeastern king county washington killing people albert berry makes the first parachute jump from a moving airplane the republic of china joins the universal postal union the u s government releases the unencrypted text of the zimmermann telegram to the public march st movement begins in korea the son of charles lindbergh charles augustus lindbergh iii is kidnapped the hoover dam is completed a strike occurs aboard the s s california leading to the demise of the international seamen s union and the creation of the national maritime union a japanese imperial army ammunition dump explodes at hirakata osaka japan killing trans canada air lines forerunner of air canada begins transcontinental operations between vancouver and montreal world war ii bulgaria signs the tripartite pact allying itself with the axis powers w nv now known as wsm fm begins operations in nashville tennessee becoming the first fm radio station in the u s world war ii battle of bismarck sea begins the bank of england is nationalised the international monetary fund begins financial operations cold war klaus fuchs is convicted of spying for the soviet union by disclosing top secret atomic bomb data joseph stalin suffers a stroke and collapses he dies four days later nuclear testing the castle bravo a megaton hydrogen bomb is detonated on bikini atoll in the pacific ocean resulting in the worst radioactive contamination ever caused by the united states puerto rican nationalists attack the united states capitol building injuring five representatives the international air transport association finalizes a draft of the radiotelephony spelling alphabet for the international civil aviation organization formation of the national people s army samuel alphonsus stritch is appointed pro prefect of the propagation of faith and thus becomes the first american member of the roman curia turkish passenger ship uskudar capsizes and sinks at izmit bay kocaeli turkey killing at least president of the united states john f kennedy establishes the peace corps uganda becomes self governing and holds its first elections american airlines flight crashes on take off in new york villarrica volcano begins a strombolian eruption causing lahas that destroy half of the town of coaripe venera soviet space probe crashes on venus becoming the first spacecraft to land on another planet s surface the ba ath party takes power in syria a bomb explodes in a men s room in the united states capitol the weather underground claims responsibility president of pakistan yahya khan indefinitely postpones the pending national assembly session precipitating massive civil disobedience in east pakistan the thai province of yasothon is created after being split off from the ubon ratchathani province black september storms the saudi embassy in khartoum sudan resulting in the assassination of three western hostages watergate scandal seven are indicted for their role in the watergate break in and charged with conspiracy to obstruct justice provisional irish republican army member bobby sands begins his hunger strike in hm prison maze the united states becomes a member of the berne convention for the protection of literary and artistic works steve jackson games is raided by the united states secret service prompting the later formation of the electronic frontier foundation bosnia and herzegovina declares its independence from socialist federal republic of yugoslavia prime minister of poland waldemar pawlak resigns from parliament and is replaced by ex communist józef oleksy yahoo was incorporated the constitution of finland is rewritten hans blix assumes the position of executive chairman of unmovic u s invasion of afghanistan operation anaconda begins in eastern afghanistan the envisat environmental satellite successfully reaches an orbit kilometers miles above the earth on its th launch carrying the heaviest payload to date at kilograms tons the peseta is discontinued as official currency of spain and is replaced by the euro management of the united states customs service and the united states secret service move to the united states department of homeland security the international criminal court holds its inaugural session in the hague mohammed bahr al uloum becomes president of iraq the death penalty for juveniles is revoked in united states english language wikipedia reaches its one millionth article jordanhill railway station tornadoes break out across the southern united states killing at least eight of the deaths are at a high school in enterprise alabama squatters are evicted from ungdomshuset in copenhagen denmark provoking the march denmark riots the armenian police clashed with peaceful opposition rally protesting against allegedly fraudulent presidential elections killing at least people births martial latin poet d isabel of coimbra queen of portugal d sandro botticelli italian painter d lorenzo de medici italian statesman d king ladislaus ii of bohemia and hungary d angela merici italian nun d rudolph goclenius german philosopher d jean charles de la faille flemish mathematician d john pell english mathematician d samuel werenfels swiss theologian d caroline of ansbach wife of george ii of great britain d william cushing nd chief justice of the united states d franois nicolas leonard buzot french revolutionary d franois séverin marceau desgraviers french general d javiera carrera chilean aristoctratic woman sister of josé miguel carrera d wilford woodruff fourth president of the church of jesus christ of latter day saints d frédéric chopin polish composer d augustus pugin english born architect d giovanni duprè italian sculptor d joseph hubert reinkens german catholic bishop d william dean howells american writer historian and politician d nicholaos gysis greek painter d augustus saint gaudens irish born american sculptor d théophile delcassé french statesman d georg simmel german sociologist and philosopher d alexander golovin russian painter d abe iso japanese politician d ben harney american composer and ragtime pi